mean to be American?

00:03:30.250 --> 00:03:32.760
What does it mean to
be Asian-American?

00:03:32.760 --> 00:03:35.270
What does it mean when
you are "the other"?

00:03:35.270 --> 00:03:39.430
What does it mean when you
don't look like everybody else?

00:03:39.430 --> 00:03:42.210
