00:03:44.050 --> 00:03:46.190
Or the religion that
you practice?

00:03:46.190 --> 00:03:48.630
Or the gender that
you identify with?

00:03:48.630 --> 00:03:51.280
These are some of the topics
that are super important,

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:54.620
