the legacies that we all stand

00:51:14.070 --> 00:51:18.690
on right now, the writers,
the family members,

00:51:18.690 --> 00:51:22.900
the letter writers, the heroes
that have come before us,

00:51:22.900 --> 00:51:26.040
who I think we're
constantly thinking of in --

00:51:26.040 --> 00:51:28.460
