a knack for bringing people

01:35:21.600 --> 01:35:23.770
and communities together.

01:35:23.770 --> 01:35:28.140
She is also a self-proclaimed
lover of science

01:35:28.140 --> 01:35:31.590
and behind the scenes
fan of McCobb.

01:35:31.590 --> 01:35:32.890
A scholar and writer

01:35:32.890 --> 01:35:36.340
who celebrates tradition
while reveling in play.

01:35:36.340 --> 01:35:39.280
A devotee to her students,
and one of my dearest

01:35:39.280 --> 01:35:42.040
and most cherished cohorts.

01:35:42.040 --> 01:35:43.760
After asking me, I
