02:50:43.300 --> 02:50:49.900
"A girl stalked a
sheep in a field.

02:50:49.900 --> 02:50:54.960
The sheep began to bleed
and the whole field smelled

02:50:54.960 --> 02:50:56.880
like carnage.

02:50:56.880 --> 02:51:02.200
A butcher had moved in
and slaughtered the sheep.

02:51:02.200 --> 02:51:05.870
Red, the stain on her dress.

02:51:05.870 --> 02:51:08.400
Empty, her basket.

02:51:08.400 --> 02:51:13.700
The depletion of resources
winter sowed??the house

02:51:13.700 --> 02:51:17.370
