Islamic history,

02:51:33.640 --> 02:51:36.440
the origin of arithmetic.

02:51:36.440 --> 02:51:40.320
The stain turned
the girl into a lady

02:51:40.320 --> 02:51:45.230
in her country's blighted
first-world landscape.

02:51:45.230 --> 02:51:52.020
