for water, it rusted.

02:51:57.720 --> 02:51:59.590
She grew cold.

02:51:59.590 --> 02:52:01.290
She grew weary.

02:52:01.290 --> 02:52:03.360
She grew sad.

02:52:03.360 --> 02:52:08.520
If only she could ban
the butcher in solidarity

02:52:08.520 --> 02:52:13.920
with the bad children,
the refugees and outcasts.

02:52:13.920 --> 02:52:20.190
Instead she drove into the city,
the urban sprawl swallowing her.

02:52:20.190 --> 02:52:25.360
She went into a store, got
caught stealing a candy bar.

02:52:25.360 --> 02:52:30.800
Surveillance footage
showed she had no remorse.

02:52:30.800 --> 02:52:35.760
