chocolate, subsidized?

02:52:40.130 --> 02:52:46.980
Then she remembered prisoners,
their tombstones unmarked.

02:52:46.980 --> 02:52:52.480
A cop arrested her, trapped her
in the back of the police van.

02:52:52.480 --> 02:52:57.800
Trillions of atoms
spinning inside her body,

02:52:57.800 --> 02:53:03.370
an unrealized commodity
for strange men's agendas.

02:53:03.370 --> 02:53:09.640
Order, dystopia, blueprint
of urban catastrophe.

02:53:09.640 --> 02:53:15.020
The streets, without
strangers, all barren.

02:53:15.020 --> 02:53:20.570
The trees, without
protection, all windswept."

